{"tid":2280032,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★5G 技術質素低劣，韓國超過 56 萬用戶重回 4G 網絡","createTime":"2020-11-10T07:54:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T09:19:48.000Z","uid":19454,"like":43,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"141e846c56b956bf4999d1d8a9aba95dd89e2e30","tid":2280032,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T07:54:11.000Z","msg":"韓國作為全球首個推出民用 5G 服務的國家，至今已經超過一年半，理應服務更加成熟可靠。然而並非每一名使用 5G 服務的消費者都感到滿意，韓國廣播和通訊委員會有成員表示，由於<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"> 5G 服務質量低劣</span></strong>、覆蓋不足和收費高昂而不滿，轉回使用 4G 服務的人不少。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據這名委員洪貞敏提供的資料，截至今年 8 月底，跟電訊商 SK Telecom、KT 和 LG Uplus 取消 5G 合約，重新回到 4G 的用戶佔 6.5%，實際人數超過 562,656 人。洪貞敏表示更改合約的程序繁複，但消費者還是因為對 5G 服務的諸多不滿而堅持要轉回 4G 服務。<br />\n<br />\n除了上述種種原因，亦有用戶投訴使用 5G 會導致手機電池消耗更快。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/11/10/poor-5g-connectivity-disappoints-south-korean-users/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F11%2F10%2Fpoor-5g-connectivity-disappoints-south-korean-users%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=dtUYnMymWvCkGCbOKSm7Ig%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=b9b32c39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/11/10/poor-5g-connectivity-disappoints-south-korean-users/mobile-phone/</a>"},{"pid":"2060143f3037c23777759029641ebdc9b4495066","tid":2280032,"uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T07:54:50.000Z","msg":"5G 白老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98abe9b4263abadbd97c89e21f406b70c7403bc7","tid":2280032,"uid":26333,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T07:56:53.000Z","msg":"，實際人數超過 562,656 隻白老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0e8d03f1af35a715e672adc6fd0401072702ebc","tid":2280032,"uid":19454,"like":5,